717222f-a.title: Manhattan: Broadway - Reade Street
717222f-a.text:
Broadway, north from Reade Street, showing prominently, the
16-story Central Syndicate Building, at the N.E. corner of Pearl
Street, and beyond that (building with clock tower) the New York
Life Insurance Company Building, fro Catherine Lane to Leonard
Street.
April 18, 1937
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
